{"tid":1835204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根據張建宗，陳肇始見記者狂咳一事，小弟有個見解","createTime":"2020-01-22T18:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T21:05:20.000Z","uid":127735,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd84dd46a4af6ffe7dafc2b5e48d193edcd5484","tid":1835204,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"為免比人話分化，幫政府洗白，請容許我先帶個頭盔：<br />\n<br />\n港共政府永不超生，三萬黑警齊落地獄<br />\n以下內容<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">非</span></strong></span>為政府洗白言論，純屬個人睇法<br />\n<br />\n我唔針對人，我只係針對件事黎睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟睇過呢兩位港共傀儡見記者時候既片段，發覺佢地暗示緊比香港人聽，武漢肺炎已經殺到埋黎，香港有可能會收留極多中國人黎香港求醫，港共政府當然無得Say no，因為呀爺叫到，唔該醒既就自求多福保護好自己，但因為林奠同中共封曬口唔比講出黎，兩位港共傀儡唯有用行動黎暗示比香港人聽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試問有幾何香港啲官見記者既時候會狂咳？你答唔答到我有邊次係咁？最多未係口疾疾咁講東東吸吸中吸東吸綜合症，個名又的確難講既。但「咳」呢回事，要扮好容易，同時真係咳都好難忍，一定咳到破肺咁濟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時間，呢個亦都係拉攏藍絲既絕好機會，你可能會話拉條鐵咩，一早斷曬脈啦。我同你講，唔係！藍絲唔怕人地損失就最怕自己有損失。肺炎呀，死人嫁！人人恐慌呀，番工每分每秒都驚自己中招呀！示範左你睇啦，再配合埋「新春免費行港豬澳大橋」「高鐵唔洗填健康申報表」呢類新聞，就可以加強佢地既自私意識，咁當然呢類野係邊個做決定？咪係政府囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我再次重申，唔係要幫港共政府洗白，我只對事不對人。我就唔知啲官見記者狂咳對上一次係幾時啦，可能我年記仲細唔知掛，有既就請提出話比我知我係鳩嗡，等香港人叫做有個安心，希望我講既唔係真。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，全民口罩，有賴你我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然，光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff22cac8ce574147e4722d500a04188d814e56c","tid":1835204,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77ab518ffe957924c26934573d848dddef5df75","tid":1835204,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"無人覆我，希望我係鳩嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b965ef3e66c8307c44bc1b6612adff1f0c6057","tid":1835204,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫你推"},{"pid":"462c07fea4f6dac4d2489fb58daada78f12bc551","tid":1835204,"uid":139450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"港共前線好多暗黃"},{"pid":"beb40dcd7470ae3725bd472f41e96569e50f75fd","tid":1835204,"uid":131259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:22:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得如果要放風佢地仲有好多方法"},{"pid":"2cb05f1221c78f2dc5cd8bc537847f85a9b43d45","tid":1835204,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"beb40dcd7470ae3725bd472f41e96569e50f75fd","tid":1835204,"uid":131259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:22:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得如果要放風佢地仲有好多方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"例如？"},{"pid":"f73669f122081875cd376fae90c001a4b59fc1c3","tid":1835204,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"462c07fea4f6dac4d2489fb58daada78f12bc551","tid":1835204,"uid":139450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"港共前線好多暗黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"對事不對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e649256a5a6b7f2a0d40709377ff1177cc65eb87","tid":1835204,"uid":235890,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:29:36.000Z","msg":"多鳩餘 你覺得呢堆高官會有惻隱之心同你放水咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你呢七個月訓著左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"